# TwinCAT FBD/FUP Migrator Safety

> All general migration safety rules are defined in `twincat3-migration-safety.mdc`. This file adds FBD-specific notes only.

## FBD-Specific Notes

- TODO markers use the format `TODO [FBD Migration]`
- JMP targets are marked as TODO and require manual IF/ELSE conversion
- The tool skips CFC, SFC, and IL implementations automatically
- R_TRIG / F_TRIG from InputFlags are auto-generated as VAR declarations
